            <paragraph>A ParallaxLayer must be the child of a <reference internal="True" refuri="class_parallaxbackground#class-parallaxbackground"><inline classes="std std-ref">ParallaxBackground</inline></reference> node. Each ParallaxLayer can be set to move at different speeds relative to the camera movement or the <reference internal="True" refuri="class_parallaxbackground#class-parallaxbackground-property-scroll-offset"><inline classes="std std-ref">ParallaxBackground.scroll_offset</inline></reference> value.</paragraph>
            <paragraph>This node's children will be affected by its scroll offset.</paragraph>
            <paragraph><strong>Note:</strong> Any changes to this node's position and scale made after it enters the scene will be ignored.</paragraph>
